{"tid":2366242,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"被指邊開會邊揸車 郭偉强未有否認 稱已盡快找位置停車","createTime":"2021-01-14T10:29:46.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-14T11:21:56.000Z","uid":240362,"like":2,"dislike":8,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"a475646b305d24f71e6f3bf7bcfd3d43994e1ac8","tid":2366242,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-14T10:29:46.000Z","msg":"立法會昨日通過議案，多個事務委員會、法案委員會可以視像方式舉行會議。立法會房屋事務委員會今（14 日）首次以 zoom 開會，多名議員疑似身處車內，其中工聯會郭偉強的畫面更多次出現安全帶、吊飾等，並出現光暗變化，疑是邊駕駛車輛邊使用電子器材 zoom，有違規之嫌。郭偉強其後在 facebook 回應事件未有否認揸車，僅稱「大家放心，已盡快在適當位置停車繼續會議」。<br />\n<br />\n郭偉強又稱，「天氣寒冷，車上暖氣是我的避寒中心。左撲右撲都是為社區服務，肖馬自然馬不停蹄？大家都要注意路上安全呀！」<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E7%AB%8B%E6%B3%95%E6%9C%83%E5%A7%94%E5%93%A1%E6%9C%83-zoom-%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83-%E7%96%91%E9%82%8A%E9%96%8B%E6%9C%83%E9%82%8A%E6%8F%B8%E8%BB%8A-%E9%83%AD%E5%81%89%E5%BC%B7-%E5%B7%B2%E7%9B%A1%E5%BF%AB%E6%89%BE%E4%BD%8D%E7%BD%AE%E5%81%9C%E8%BB%8A/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-zoom-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2582%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2582%258A%25E6%258F%25B8%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%2589%25BE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BB%258A%2F&d=qXcR1A%2FTALq%2FhnoNE0cJVQUT8Qe%2F7ZKEe33%2FbaB1Hos%3D&h=18bf347e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E7%25AB%258B%25E6%25B3%2595%25E6%259C%2583%25E5%25A7%2594%25E5%2593%25A1%25E6%259C%2583-zoom-%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583-%25E7%2596%2591%25E9%2582%258A%25E9%2596%258B%25E6%259C%2583%25E9%2582%258A%25E6%258F%25B8%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E9%2583%25AD%25E5%2581%2589%25E5%25BC%25B7-%25E5%25B7%25B2%25E7%259B%25A1%25E5%25BF%25AB%25E6%2589%25BE%25E4%25BD%258D%25E7%25BD%25AE%25E5%2581%259C%25E8%25BB%258